---
title: Cal Smart Roasted Barramundi with Veggie Bulgur and Lemon Aioli
description: Simplicity at its best! A light and bright meal of perfectly seasoned barramundi gets a dollop of lemon aioli, served on a bed of roasted zucchini and peppers tossed with bulgur.

